# Changelog

## [0.4.0] - 2022-06-27

### Added
- getter for internal token-request (will be moved to libMisakaGuard in the near future)

### Changed
- reworked client-handling for better usability and stability
- updated error-loggin


## [0.3.0] - 2022-02-13

### Added
- allow multiple servers at the same time
- add message-forwarding to stream-messages
- send error-messages to sagiri
- add generic data-transfer, which are basically request-response-messages


## [0.2.0] - 2022-01-09

### Added
- reconnect-functionality for connections
- jwt-token validation for incoming messages
- use endpoint-definitions to map requests to targets

### Changed
- updated initializing process

### Fixed
- different fixes to improve stability


## [0.1.0] - 2021-09-26

### Added
- content of the old libKitsunemimiSakuraMessaging-repo
    -  basic project-specific wrapper for libKitsunemimiSakuraNetwork

